import Form from "../components/Form";
import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";
import TextField from "@mui/material/TextField";
import Table from "../components/Table";
import { Button, FormControl, MenuItem, Select } from "@mui/material";
import { useState } from "react";

const initialStudent = {
  name: "",
  lastname: "",
  email: "",
  dni: "",
  phone: "",
  institute: "",
  career: "",
};

export const Student = () => {
  const [student, setStudent] = useState(initialStudent);

  return (
    <>
      <Form title="Estudiante">
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField
              value={student.name}
              onChange={(event) =>
                setStudent({ ...student, name: event.target.value })
              }
              label="Nombre"
              variant="outlined"
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField label="Apellido" variant="outlined" />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField label="Email" variant="outlined" />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField label="DNI" variant="outlined" />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField label="Celular" variant="outlined" />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl>
              <Select label="Instituto">
                <MenuItem value={10}>Valle Grande</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value={12}>Condoray</MenuItem>
              </Select>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl>
              <Select label="Carrera">
                <MenuItem value={10}>Analisis de sistemas</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value={12}>Agraria</MenuItem>
              </Select>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Button variant="contained">Enviar</Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Form>
      <Table />
    </>
  );
};

export default Student;
